column2: "There...? Or is it there? ...Why can't this body sense it?!"
"The place where my power was broken before, it should be here!"
"Why can't I detect my own power...?!"
"...You appear greatly angered, Dark Falz. No... Big sis Yuku."
"Tsk! ARKS...! Stop calling to me in that disgusting manner!"
"I won't stop... like hell I'd give up now. Until big sis remembers everything, I'll call out as many times as I have to!"
"Please calm down. Your voice is getting to her."
"It's different from the me that was chasing illusions. If you keep at it, you'll surely connect with her."
"Partner... Heh, that's right! It's still too early to give in!"
"Alright! Let's surpass these guys and find big sis Yuku again!"
